examples.en: I spent most of the day chauffeuring the kids around.
A chauffeur opened the door of the limousine for the grand lady.
She was chauffeured to the airport.
He chauffeured his client to the hotel.
Mum was cook, chauffeur, nurse, and entertainer all rolled into one.
The limousine chauffeur was easily distinguished from the cab drivers by his livery.
